1
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:01,000
The Late Emperor

2
00:01:01,679 --> 00:01:02,759
didn't die of rage.

3
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:03,560
It was

4
00:01:04,079 --> 00:01:04,799
a strange poison.

5
00:01:05,879 --> 00:01:06,680
What?

6
00:01:08,959 --> 00:01:10,840
Until the real culprit is found,

7
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:11,560
this matter

8
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:14,439
must stay between the two of us.

9
00:01:26,439 --> 00:01:28,760
Dai Anna's farewell show tickets on sale!

10
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:29,680
Limited quantity!

11
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:30,719
First come, first served!

12
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:36,439
Hey!

13
00:01:36,959 --> 00:01:38,079
You got grease all over me!

14
00:01:40,319 --> 00:01:41,079
What's wrong with you?

15
00:01:41,079 --> 00:01:42,920
You bump into someone and don't apologize?

16
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:43,959
I'm sorry.

17
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,359
I'm sorry.

18
00:01:46,079 --> 00:01:47,239
I told him to apologize,

19
00:01:47,359 --> 00:01:48,159
not you.

20
00:01:48,439 --> 00:01:48,680
Hey!

21
00:01:49,439 --> 00:01:49,719
Young lady,

22
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:50,680
what's that supposed to mean?

23
00:01:50,959 --> 00:01:51,159
Hey,

24
00:01:51,159 --> 00:01:51,519
nothing.

25
00:01:51,599 --> 00:01:52,480
Nothing at all.

26
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:53,840
We're buying this meat.

27
00:01:54,079 --> 00:01:54,400
I'm buying it.

28
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,280
Huh?

29
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:58,280
Fine.

30
00:01:58,599 --> 00:01:59,280
It's yours.

31
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:00,680
Smart move.

32
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:02,840
How can someone so savage become Empress?

33
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:06,680
What Prince wants such an unfeminine wife?

34
00:02:07,079 --> 00:02:07,319
Ha!

35
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,280
Then tell me,

36
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,360
what counts as feminine?

37
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:13,159
Look,

38
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,159
at least something like this.

39
00:02:16,639 --> 00:02:18,240
Your taste is the problem.

40
00:02:19,080 --> 00:02:20,080
Says who?

41
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:20,599
Like this,

42
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,439
that's what feminine looks like!

43
00:02:24,639 --> 00:02:26,639
Would you like an effeminate man?

44
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,240
Me?

45
00:02:28,479 --> 00:02:29,479
Of course I would.

46
00:02:30,719 --> 00:02:32,280
I'm not as superficial as you.

47
00:02:32,639 --> 00:02:33,639
Judging people by their looks.

48
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,159
Hey,

49
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:39,879
where are you going?

50
00:02:40,039 --> 00:02:41,439
To see Dai Wang, of course!

51
00:02:54,439 --> 00:02:55,280
Prince,

52
00:02:55,439 --> 00:02:56,879
Court Emissary Qi Zhi

53
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:59,280
and Princess Ouyang Yan seek an audience.

54
00:03:05,719 --> 00:03:06,520
Send them in.

55
00:03:07,879 --> 00:03:08,719
Greetings, Prince.

56
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,120
Flowers.

57
00:03:12,639 --> 00:03:13,560
Sorry about that.

58
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:14,439
Heh heh heh.

59
00:03:14,719 --> 00:03:15,719
You came all this way

60
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,719
and even brought gifts.

61
00:03:17,039 --> 00:03:18,319
You two are too kind.

62
00:03:18,319 --> 00:03:19,120
Ah.

63
00:03:19,639 --> 00:03:20,439
Oh.

64
00:03:21,319 --> 00:03:22,360
Hey.

65
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:22,800
The meat, yes.

66
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,080
The chicken, no.

67
00:03:26,159 --> 00:03:27,879
Who knew the Princess of Yan

68
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:29,639
had fallen on such hard times.

69
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,639
Who's fallen on hard times?

70
00:03:33,439 --> 00:03:34,639
If you mean me, just say so.

71
00:03:34,759 --> 00:03:36,039
Don't drag Yan into this.

72
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:38,879
My apologies.

73
00:03:40,759 --> 00:03:42,240
May I ask what brings you two

74
00:03:42,639 --> 00:03:43,719
to see me today?

75
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:44,319
Oh.

76
00:03:44,439 --> 00:03:45,159
Well,

77
00:03:46,919 --> 00:03:48,039
The Crown Prince sent us from the palace

78
00:03:48,039 --> 00:03:49,439
to find a suitable heir to the throne.

79
00:03:49,439 --> 00:03:50,120
Passing through Dai Cheng,

80
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:50,879
we noticed its people

81
00:03:50,879 --> 00:03:52,240
living in peace and prosperity.

82
00:03:52,439 --> 00:03:53,479
Surely Dai Wang has the talent to govern.

83
00:03:53,639 --> 00:03:55,080
Please return and ascend the throne.

84
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:55,439
Your turn.

85
00:03:55,879 --> 00:03:56,439
I'm not saying it.

86
00:03:59,879 --> 00:04:01,319
As for becoming Emperor,

87
00:04:01,439 --> 00:04:02,280
I'll pass.

88
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:04,879
I've long heard that to be Emperor,

89
00:04:04,879 --> 00:04:06,759
one must marry the Princess of Yan.

90
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:09,080
That's more than I can handle.

91
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,639
Who'd want to marry you anyway?

92
00:04:11,919 --> 00:04:12,719
Hey, hey!

93
00:04:13,639 --> 00:04:14,280
Show them out.

94
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:15,560
Prince!

95
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:15,840
But...

96
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,079
This is still negotiable!

97
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:18,040
Emissaries,

98
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:19,079
this way, please.

99
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:23,920
Dai Anna is so popular.

100
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:28,040
Do you think Dai Wang likes her too?

101
00:04:30,439 --> 00:04:31,240
What did you say?

102
00:04:33,439 --> 00:04:34,240
What did I say?

103
00:04:40,199 --> 00:04:42,040
He really might have feelings for her.

104
00:04:43,319 --> 00:04:44,120
Hey!

105
00:04:44,879 --> 00:04:45,920
What are you spacing out for?

106
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:47,279
Next!

107
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:49,040
Didn't think you'd actually be useful.

108
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:50,720
Well...

109
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,480
Of course I am.

110
00:04:54,639 --> 00:04:56,040
So, what did you come up with?

111
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:59,879
I may have a way to approach Dai Wang.

112
00:05:04,279 --> 00:05:05,160
Then why get in line?

113
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,639
I have a rough idea.

114
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:08,279
Everyone!

115
00:05:08,279 --> 00:05:09,040
What idea?

116
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:10,480
Everyone!

117
00:05:10,759 --> 00:05:12,319
Today's tickets are sold out.

118
00:05:12,439 --> 00:05:13,839
Please come back tomorrow.

119
00:05:14,199 --> 00:05:14,759
Aw...

120
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:15,600
Hey!

121
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,720
Everyone, everyone, everyone!

122
00:05:16,759 --> 00:05:18,720
I've got two tickets right here.

123
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,000
Who wants them?

124
00:05:19,639 --> 00:05:20,639
Who wants them?

125
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:21,839
Me, me, me!

126
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:23,439
I want them too!

127
00:05:23,839 --> 00:05:24,639
How much?

128
00:05:24,639 --> 00:05:24,959
Sir!

129
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,199
These tickets...

130
00:05:26,279 --> 00:05:27,120
there are only two left.

131
00:05:27,319 --> 00:05:28,480
Highest bidder wins.

132
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,160
Starting price...

133
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:30,279
one hundred taels.

134
00:05:30,839 --> 00:05:31,399
One hundred taels!

135
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,959
I bid two hundred taels!

136
00:05:33,079 --> 00:05:33,959
Two hundred and one taels!

137
00:05:34,279 --> 00:05:35,160
Two hundred and one!

138
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:35,879
I bid three hundred taels!

139
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:36,959
Three hundred taels!

140
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,040
Three hundred and one!

141
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:38,959
Three hundred and one taels!

142
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:39,480
Are you insane?

143
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:39,720
Five hundred taels!

144
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:41,480
Five hundred taels!

145
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,120
Five hundred and one!

146
00:05:43,639 --> 00:05:44,439
Are you out of your mind?

147
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:46,519
That's all the travel money we have!

148
00:05:46,639 --> 00:05:47,040
It's fine.

149
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,560
If we can convince Dai Wang to be Emperor,

150
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,639
who needs travel money?

151
00:05:49,879 --> 00:05:51,079
Give me that one tael in your hand.

152
00:05:51,079 --> 00:05:51,879
With my five hundred taels...

153
00:05:52,279 --> 00:05:53,079
No way.

154
00:05:53,279 --> 00:05:53,720
Hurry up!

155
00:05:53,839 --> 00:05:54,839
If someone outbids us, we're done for.

156
00:05:55,879 --> 00:05:56,279
Anyone else?

157
00:05:56,279 --> 00:05:57,040
Wait!

158
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,120
I bid ten thousand taels!

159
00:05:58,879 --> 00:05:59,839
Ten thousand taels!

160
00:06:00,319 --> 00:06:01,079
Sold, sold!

161
00:06:03,839 --> 00:06:04,759
You're all crazy!

162
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,560
So are you.

163
00:06:07,839 --> 00:06:10,360
This is Miss Dai Anna's farewell performance!

164
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:13,519
10,000 taels for one last glimpse of her,

165
00:06:13,759 --> 00:06:15,279
it's totally worth it!

166
00:06:15,279 --> 00:06:16,079
Haha!

167
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:21,720
What's so magical about this Dai Anna?

168
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,639
Everyone's so obsessed with her.

169
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:29,439
I'm pretty sure I'm right.

170
00:06:29,639 --> 00:06:30,480
Right about what?

171
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,720
Take another close look at this poster.

172
00:06:33,879 --> 00:06:34,920
Notice anything?

173
00:06:39,319 --> 00:06:39,959
Look at the face.

174
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,560
Now look at the shoes.

175
00:06:49,519 --> 00:06:50,160
Oh!

176
00:06:50,399 --> 00:06:51,079
Dai Wang!

177
00:06:51,959 --> 00:06:52,319
Don't say it!

178
00:06:52,319 --> 00:06:53,079
Keep your voice down.

179
00:07:02,639 --> 00:07:03,480
Dai Wang!

180
00:07:05,319 --> 00:07:05,560
You!

181
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:06,160
You two!

182
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,439
You're Dai Anna, aren't you?

183
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:12,040
Trespassing the manor in broad daylight...

184
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,160
what's the punishment for that?

185
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:14,879
If you dare arrest us,

186
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:17,319
we'll tell everyone you're Dai Anna.

187
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:19,839
How will you face the city's people then?

188
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:20,439
You...

189
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:21,279
Hey.

190
00:07:21,319 --> 00:07:21,839
Dai Wang.

191
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:25,160
We sincerely want you to return as Emperor.

192
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,639
You have the talent to rule,

193
00:07:27,639 --> 00:07:28,480
and the knowledge.

194
00:07:28,839 --> 00:07:29,879
Come with us.

195
00:07:30,879 --> 00:07:31,839
I won't go.

196
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:33,879
If you don't come,

197
00:07:34,279 --> 00:07:36,720
I'll tell everyone you're Dai Anna.

198
00:07:37,839 --> 00:07:39,279
You judge me without knowing anything!

199
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:51,959
Mother

200
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,240
What's wrong?

201
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,319
Say whatever you want.

202
00:08:00,839 --> 00:08:01,399
Regardless,

203
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:02,959
this performance,

204
00:08:03,199 --> 00:08:04,279
I must see it through.

205
00:08:05,279 --> 00:08:07,279
If it's something you absolutely must do,

206
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:10,560
then there must be a compelling reason.

207
00:08:13,079 --> 00:08:14,639
Is it for your mother?

208
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:17,040
How did you know?

209
00:08:17,079 --> 00:08:17,879
I...

210
00:08:18,839 --> 00:08:20,360
And when you touched me earlier...

211
00:08:20,439 --> 00:08:21,480
I-I-I just guessed.

212
00:08:22,759 --> 00:08:24,360
Prince, if you trust us,

213
00:08:24,639 --> 00:08:26,360
we're willing to help you.

214
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:28,160
I didn't agree to that.

215
00:08:33,279 --> 00:08:34,120
My Royal Mother's

216
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:37,120
greatest wish in life

217
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:40,120
was to put on a show of her own.

218
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,639
But until the day she passed away,

219
00:08:44,039 --> 00:08:45,279
she never fulfilled that wish.

220
00:08:47,639 --> 00:08:49,240
Though I'm not a daughter,

221
00:08:50,039 --> 00:08:51,399
I still want to use my own way

222
00:08:52,039 --> 00:08:53,320
to fulfill her dying wish.

223
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:56,440
I never would've guessed

224
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,559
you were such a devoted son.

225
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:00,679
No.

226
00:09:01,679 --> 00:09:03,519
I want to return to a normal life,

227
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:06,679
so this will be my final performance.

228
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:13,879
Emissaries,

229
00:09:15,279 --> 00:09:17,480
I hope you can keep this secret for me.

230
00:09:19,759 --> 00:09:20,080
Mm.

231
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:20,879
Mm.

232
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:21,960
Prince,

233
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,720
after the performance is over,

234
00:09:24,279 --> 00:09:25,840
come back and be Emperor.

235
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:30,840
And you must take her as your Empress.

236
00:09:32,879 --> 00:09:33,159
That's right.

237
00:09:33,759 --> 00:09:34,120
You must.

238
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:34,480
Absolutely.

239
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:38,840
Fine.

240
00:09:39,679 --> 00:09:40,559
I promise you.

241
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,759
As soon as the performance ends,

242
00:09:43,039 --> 00:09:44,279
I'll return to the palace with you,

243
00:09:44,919 --> 00:09:45,960
and make you my Empress.

244
00:09:47,559 --> 00:09:48,759
But as I just said,

245
00:09:49,279 --> 00:09:51,320
since this is my final solo performance,

246
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,279
regarding the show,

247
00:09:53,279 --> 00:09:54,639
I've run into some difficulties

248
00:09:54,879 --> 00:09:56,360
that I need your help to solve.

249
00:09:58,039 --> 00:10:00,919
You solved my huge personal problem,

250
00:10:01,039 --> 00:10:01,679
so whatever you need, just say it.

251
00:10:01,919 --> 00:10:02,279
Just say it.

252
00:10:04,279 --> 00:10:06,080
Since there are many costumes this time,

253
00:10:06,279 --> 00:10:08,080
I need you to smuggle them out

254
00:10:08,639 --> 00:10:09,960
and deliver them to Starlight Theater.

255
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:13,039
The shoes my Royal Mother left are broken.

256
00:10:13,039 --> 00:10:14,279
I can't leave the manor easily,

257
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,840
so I hope you can get them repaired.

258
00:10:17,679 --> 00:10:18,919
It's just a few clothes, right?

259
00:10:18,919 --> 00:10:19,440
Don't worry.

260
00:10:19,919 --> 00:10:20,720
Leave it to me.

261
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:21,519
Leave it to her.

262
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:25,240
Dry weather, beware of fire!

263
00:10:25,679 --> 00:10:27,960
Guard against fire and thieves, lock your doors!

264
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:29,080
Hey!

265
00:10:29,879 --> 00:10:31,679
Have you no conscience?

266
00:10:32,039 --> 00:10:32,679
Hey,

267
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:34,159
I can't climb walls,

268
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:35,480
I don't know martial arts,

269
00:10:35,759 --> 00:10:38,279
and I never said "leave it to me."

270
00:10:38,679 --> 00:10:40,679
Whoever took the job handles it.

271
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,759
You...

272
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:44,039
Post more guards around the manor for now.

273
00:10:45,039 --> 00:10:46,200
I want to see

274
00:10:46,679 --> 00:10:48,120
exactly who's been stealing my clothes.

275
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,080
Yes, sir.

276
00:10:53,159 --> 00:10:53,960
Go!

277
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,120
Let's go.

278
00:11:00,679 --> 00:11:01,480
Halt!

279
00:11:03,559 --> 00:11:04,360
Come on!

280
00:11:09,679 --> 00:11:10,480
Stop right there!

281
00:11:11,519 --> 00:11:11,720
You!

282
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:12,360
Halt!

283
00:11:16,679 --> 00:11:17,480
Stop!

284
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,279
Run!

285
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:23,399
Boss,

286
00:11:23,399 --> 00:11:24,039
I need these shoes repaired.

287
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:30,960
Oh my

288
00:11:31,399 --> 00:11:32,679
These shoes are completely worn out.

289
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:33,600
You still want them repaired?

290
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:34,480
Just

291
00:11:34,759 --> 00:11:35,200
buy a new pair

292
00:11:35,639 --> 00:11:36,679
I have some right here.

293
00:11:36,679 --> 00:11:37,840
One tael of silver a pair

294
00:11:37,919 --> 00:11:38,480
Want them?

295
00:11:38,679 --> 00:11:39,679
Just repair these

296
00:11:40,279 --> 00:11:41,039
Oh dear

297
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:43,240
If you want these repaired

298
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:45,679
that'll cost ten taels of silver

299
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:48,279
Repair them

300
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:49,360
Fine

301
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:50,360
I'll fix them.

302
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:54,679
Huh?

303
00:11:57,039 --> 00:11:58,240
They look so alike.

304
00:12:00,879 --> 00:12:01,840
Like what?

305
00:12:02,279 --> 00:12:02,679
Oh

306
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,440
I mean the shoes

307
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:07,039
No wonder they looked so familiar

308
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,240
Turns out

309
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:10,000
they're just like Miss Dai Anna's shoes.

310
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:10,679
Identical!

311
00:12:12,039 --> 00:12:12,600
Oh my

312
00:12:12,679 --> 00:12:14,679
There's even gold thread here

313
00:12:17,159 --> 00:12:18,720
Could these be the authentic ones?

314
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:19,480
I'll pay 100,000 taels

315
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:20,279
I want these shoes

316
00:12:20,279 --> 00:12:21,279
Why do you turn up everywhere?

317
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:23,639
A young gentleman told me

318
00:12:23,679 --> 00:12:26,320
someone repairs Miss Dai Anna's heels here.

319
00:12:26,679 --> 00:12:29,320
To get Miss Dai Anna's one-of-a-kind heels

320
00:12:29,679 --> 00:12:31,159
no price is too high

321
00:12:31,519 --> 00:12:32,960
I'll pay the 100,000 taels

322
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:33,559
Stop!

323
00:12:35,679 --> 00:12:36,919
I am a Court Emissary

324
00:12:36,919 --> 00:12:38,039
This is the Crown Prince's decree

325
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,440
Seeing this decree

326
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:41,039
is like seeing the Crown Prince himself!

327
00:12:41,039 --> 00:12:41,960
I order you all

328
00:12:42,559 --> 00:12:43,840
no one is to touch these shoes

329
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:45,840
He must've robbed Miss Dai Anna's shoes!

330
00:12:46,039 --> 00:12:47,759
Let's snatch Miss Dai Anna's shoes back!

331
00:12:48,759 --> 00:12:49,360
Stop!

332
00:12:49,559 --> 00:12:49,960
Stop!

333
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:51,039
Stop it!

334
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:53,679
You actually hit me!

335
00:12:55,279 --> 00:12:55,559
Dai Wang

336
00:12:56,279 --> 00:12:57,159
Are you done yet?

337
00:12:58,679 --> 00:12:59,360
I...

338
00:12:59,720 --> 00:13:00,840
I don't think my makeup's quite right

339
00:13:01,879 --> 00:13:03,399
I'm feeling insecure, can you wait a bit longer?

340
00:13:03,639 --> 00:13:04,639
I'm here to protect you

341
00:13:04,639 --> 00:13:04,960
What's there to fear?

342
00:13:05,240 --> 00:13:05,399
Let's go, quick

343
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:07,320
Did I bring my accessories?

344
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:07,679
Come on

345
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:08,279
Yes, you did

346
00:13:08,919 --> 00:13:10,240
I want to check the mirror one more time

347
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:11,039
Just one last look

348
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:11,679
Come on

349
00:13:11,679 --> 00:13:12,639
Stop looking

350
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,559
All right, all right

351
00:13:14,559 --> 00:13:15,320
I'll go, okay?

352
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:16,240
Don't drag me

353
00:13:16,240 --> 00:13:16,399
Go, go, go

354
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:22,039
Stop right there!

355
00:13:25,360 --> 00:13:26,240
What do I do, what do I do?

356
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:27,279
Don't let them see me. Block me!

357
00:13:27,960 --> 00:13:28,360
Block me!

358
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:29,840
Well, well.

359
00:13:30,799 --> 00:13:32,279
Got what you wanted and now you're running?

360
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:34,840
Who are you?

361
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:35,480
Hmph!

362
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:36,720
In my royal manor,

363
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:38,480
seducing my man,

364
00:13:38,519 --> 00:13:40,240
and you dare ask who I am?

365
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:42,039
The Princess Consort!

366
00:13:42,399 --> 00:13:42,799
Hey.

367
00:13:43,279 --> 00:13:44,720
If I hadn't caught you myself,

368
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:46,039
I truly wouldn't have believed

369
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:48,440
the Prince would fancy a woman like you.

370
00:13:50,480 --> 00:13:52,039
Hand over your bundle.

371
00:13:52,360 --> 00:13:53,360
Let me see for myself

372
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:55,919
what treasure my Prince stole to give you.

373
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:59,440
Who'd want your worthless junk?

374
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:02,559
This princess is destined to be Empress!

375
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:03,799
Now get out of my way!

376
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:05,480
A good dog doesn't block the road.

377
00:14:05,679 --> 00:14:06,279
What?

378
00:14:07,039 --> 00:14:08,039
You dare call me a—

379
00:14:09,039 --> 00:14:09,240
Stop!

380
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:11,039
What are you doing?

381
00:14:11,759 --> 00:14:12,559
Prince...

382
00:14:15,679 --> 00:14:17,679
You'd even disguise yourself like this

383
00:14:17,679 --> 00:14:19,679
just to elope with this little vixen?

384
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:20,440
Me?

385
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:22,480
What's wrong with me to make you do this?

386
00:14:22,879 --> 00:14:24,399
I'll make you change your mind.

387
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:24,559
Hey.

388
00:14:24,639 --> 00:14:25,080
Enough.

389
00:14:25,399 --> 00:14:25,720
Stop talking.

390
00:14:26,399 --> 00:14:26,559
Let's go.

391
00:14:29,360 --> 00:14:30,159
Prince!

392
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,240
Don't hurt her.

393
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:33,360
Don't move!

394
00:14:34,360 --> 00:14:35,559
Drop your weapons,

395
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:36,840
or I'll kill her!

396
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:38,240
I'm done for, done for, done for!

397
00:14:38,639 --> 00:14:40,360
I ruined Dai Wang's perfectly good shoes!

398
00:14:40,360 --> 00:14:41,639
How do I face him when I get back?

399
00:14:42,960 --> 00:14:43,759
Hey.

400
00:14:44,279 --> 00:14:44,799
Dai Wang.

401
00:14:45,039 --> 00:14:45,519
Look,

402
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:47,679
why don't you wear them as slippers?

403
00:14:48,759 --> 00:14:49,480
Qi Zhi!

404
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:52,039
You failed the one tiny task I gave you!

405
00:14:52,279 --> 00:14:52,440
You—

406
00:14:53,279 --> 00:14:54,039
No, Dai Wang,

407
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:55,039
Let me explain!

408
00:14:55,240 --> 00:14:56,279
I won't listen, I won't listen, I won't listen!

409
00:14:56,879 --> 00:14:57,159
Ugh.

410
00:14:57,320 --> 00:14:57,960
What a hassle.

411
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:01,519
Should I just toss it?

412
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:23,000
Now then,

413
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:24,120
it's all up to you.

414
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:24,639
Right.

415
00:15:24,759 --> 00:15:26,039
I'll lead the soldiers away.

416
00:15:26,159 --> 00:15:27,679
They definitely won't track us here.

417
00:15:28,879 --> 00:15:29,679
Hey.

418
00:15:30,679 --> 00:15:31,279
Thank you.

419
00:15:32,279 --> 00:15:32,720
All along the way,

420
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:34,279
you've done so much for me.

421
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:35,679
It's nothing.

422
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:36,440
I'm off now.

423
00:15:36,879 --> 00:15:37,159
Good luck!

424
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:41,639
And now,

425
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:44,360
let's give a warm round of applause

426
00:15:44,480 --> 00:15:46,679
to welcome our city's idol,

427
00:15:47,039 --> 00:15:48,320
the born aristocrat,

428
00:15:48,480 --> 00:15:50,320
the dazzling, ultimate heartthrob,

429
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:53,679
Miss Dai Anna!

430
00:16:00,039 --> 00:16:02,039
Our applause isn't loud enough.

431
00:16:02,399 --> 00:16:03,360
Cheer louder!

432
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:06,519
I'm here, I'm here!

433
00:16:06,840 --> 00:16:07,159
Emissary,

434
00:16:07,519 --> 00:16:08,039
you're finally here.

435
00:16:08,039 --> 00:16:08,679
Where are my shoes?

436
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:10,039
Here.

437
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:14,759
You've got to be kidding me.

438
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:16,120
These aren't my shoes.

439
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:20,840
But your mother's shoes,

440
00:16:22,039 --> 00:16:23,320
this is all that's left.

441
00:16:29,720 --> 00:16:30,519
No.

442
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:33,679
Everyone's waiting for you onstage.

443
00:16:33,799 --> 00:16:34,039
No.

444
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:35,840
I can't go on.

445
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:39,000
Everything I've done,

446
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:40,679
it was all for my mother.

447
00:16:41,519 --> 00:16:43,320
Without my mother's heels,

448
00:16:44,279 --> 00:16:45,679
none of this means anything.

449
00:16:45,679 --> 00:16:47,639
And lying to yourself does?

450
00:16:48,879 --> 00:16:49,840
What did you say?

451
00:16:51,919 --> 00:16:54,039
It seems Miss Dai Anna is a bit shy.

452
00:16:54,120 --> 00:16:56,039
Let's welcome her onstage again!

453
00:16:59,279 --> 00:16:59,759
Miss,

454
00:16:59,879 --> 00:17:00,919
the audience is getting impatient.

455
00:17:01,279 --> 00:17:07,279
Dai Anna.

456
00:17:07,359 --> 00:17:09,079
I found this inside your mother's heel.

457
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:10,160
See for yourself.

458
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:13,279
My dear Dai,

459
00:17:14,319 --> 00:17:16,119
Mother has long known

460
00:17:16,720 --> 00:17:18,319
that though you have a man's body,

461
00:17:19,079 --> 00:17:20,759
you have the heart of a girl.

462
00:17:22,240 --> 00:17:23,519
My dear Dai,

463
00:17:24,599 --> 00:17:25,039
in days to come,

464
00:17:25,319 --> 00:17:26,839
should I no longer be by your side,

465
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:29,720
I wish for you to bravely face it all,

466
00:17:30,279 --> 00:17:31,960
and do what you truly love.

467
00:17:33,039 --> 00:17:33,839
Royal Mother...

468
00:17:36,440 --> 00:17:36,960
The truth is,

469
00:17:38,319 --> 00:17:39,559
performing one hundred shows

470
00:17:40,119 --> 00:17:42,119
was never your mother's wish.

471
00:17:42,839 --> 00:17:44,400
It was your own dream, wasn't it?

472
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:45,240
Wasn't it?

473
00:17:50,039 --> 00:17:50,920
Go on, get up there.

474
00:17:55,079 --> 00:17:55,880
Stop right there!

475
00:17:56,440 --> 00:17:57,160
Don't run!

476
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:57,960
Sorry!

477
00:17:57,960 --> 00:17:58,759
Stop!

478
00:17:59,720 --> 00:18:00,519
Don't run!

479
00:18:15,119 --> 00:18:15,960
Isn't this a man?

480
00:18:16,279 --> 00:18:17,680
We came to see Dai Anna!

481
00:18:17,680 --> 00:18:18,240
Get off!

482
00:18:18,240 --> 00:18:19,039
Get off the stage!

483
00:18:22,880 --> 00:18:24,039
This is too sudden.

484
00:18:24,279 --> 00:18:25,240
I'm not ready yet.

485
00:18:25,440 --> 00:18:26,440
Dai Anna.

486
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:28,519
You can choose to lie to yourself,

487
00:18:28,799 --> 00:18:29,279
to tell yourself

488
00:18:29,279 --> 00:18:30,960
that all of this is for your mother.

489
00:18:31,119 --> 00:18:33,160
Or you can embrace who you truly are.

490
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:34,119
Put on your own shoes,

491
00:18:34,119 --> 00:18:35,519
and perform for yourself.

492
00:18:35,519 --> 00:18:40,880
Dai Anna,

493
00:18:41,359 --> 00:18:43,319
you still need some time, don't you?

494
00:18:43,599 --> 00:18:44,039
Alright.

495
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:46,480
I'll buy you some time.

496
00:18:51,079 --> 00:18:52,079
Where are you going?

497
00:18:55,440 --> 00:18:56,839
You have to believe in yourself.

498
00:18:57,640 --> 00:18:59,039
Because when you are confident,

499
00:19:01,079 --> 00:19:01,960
you are truly beautiful.

500
00:19:02,960 --> 00:19:13,000
Get off!

501
00:19:55,240 --> 00:19:55,519
Hey, hey, hey!

502
00:19:56,279 --> 00:19:57,039
Stop throwing things!

503
00:19:58,000 --> 00:19:58,680
Stop it!

504
00:21:21,119 --> 00:21:22,160
Look at you.

505
00:21:22,440 --> 00:21:23,440
Don't let their jeers get to you.

506
00:21:24,079 --> 00:21:25,960
That makeup really suits you.

507
00:21:26,279 --> 00:21:27,279
Oh, shut up.

508
00:21:27,680 --> 00:21:29,880
Dai Anna!

509
00:21:36,440 --> 00:21:37,519
Thank you, everyone.

510
00:21:37,920 --> 00:21:40,200
for coming to my 100th show today.

511
00:21:40,799 --> 00:21:41,519
Today,

512
00:21:42,119 --> 00:21:43,359
I have an announcement to make.

513
00:21:46,039 --> 00:21:47,039
Today's performance

514
00:21:47,440 --> 00:21:49,640
will be my final show as Dai Anna.

515
00:21:52,960 --> 00:21:54,160
Thank you all for the support

516
00:21:55,079 --> 00:21:56,279
you've shown me all this time.

517
00:21:57,759 --> 00:21:59,240
And thank you to my friends,

518
00:22:00,000 --> 00:22:01,400
who quietly cheered me on.

519
00:22:04,119 --> 00:22:05,079
Thank you to my mother,

520
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:07,559
for giving me the courage to be myself.

521
00:22:13,640 --> 00:22:14,640
So sudden.

522
00:22:17,680 --> 00:22:19,160
Why does she look so much like Dai Wang?

523
00:22:21,519 --> 00:22:22,359
Right, look.

524
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:26,440
Yeah.

525
00:22:28,359 --> 00:22:29,480
That's Dai Wang!

526
00:22:30,759 --> 00:22:31,119
Oh my!

527
00:22:31,680 --> 00:22:33,079
Dai Anna looks just like Dai Wang!

528
00:22:33,440 --> 00:22:34,240
Not just looks like,

529
00:22:34,519 --> 00:22:35,720
that IS Dai Wang!

530
00:22:36,319 --> 00:22:37,079
What's going on here?

531
00:22:37,079 --> 00:22:38,839
How can this be?

532
00:22:38,960 --> 00:22:39,759
That's right.

533
00:22:40,559 --> 00:22:41,720
I am Dai Wang.

534
00:22:42,680 --> 00:22:43,880
No matter what you think of me,

535
00:22:44,680 --> 00:22:45,480
from this day forward,

536
00:22:45,880 --> 00:22:48,079
I'll no longer appear as Dai Anna.

537
00:22:48,960 --> 00:22:50,839
Though this is Dai Anna's final show,

538
00:22:51,480 --> 00:22:51,880
it is also

539
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:54,640
my very first show as Dai Wang.

540
00:22:55,160 --> 00:23:00,119
Yes!

541
00:23:00,279 --> 00:23:18,079
Dai Wang!

542
00:23:20,480 --> 00:23:22,240
This Dai Wang, really.

543
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:24,119
We did him such a huge favor,

544
00:23:24,640 --> 00:23:27,000
and he didn't make me Empress as promised.

545
00:23:27,160 --> 00:23:28,039
He didn't even take the throne.

546
00:23:28,039 --> 00:23:28,519
Forget it.

547
00:23:28,599 --> 00:23:30,440
It's not like this is the first time.

548
00:23:31,039 --> 00:23:32,279
I'm actually rather surprised

549
00:23:32,319 --> 00:23:34,640
he had the guts to come clean to everyone.

550
00:23:36,440 --> 00:23:38,720
I hope everyone in town turns against him

551
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:40,680
and teaches him a real lesson.

552
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:42,119
I actually believe

553
00:23:42,119 --> 00:23:43,759
even if the whole city turns against him,

554
00:23:43,759 --> 00:23:45,960
he'll handle it with ease.

555
00:23:46,680 --> 00:23:48,160
Why are you always defending him?

556
00:23:49,359 --> 00:23:49,839
A man, a woman...

557
00:23:50,640 --> 00:23:51,079
A woman.

558
00:23:51,839 --> 00:23:53,839
Who among mortals can truly see clearly?

559
00:23:54,839 --> 00:23:55,599
Take you, for instance.

560
00:23:56,279 --> 00:23:58,079
Besides your face, what makes you a woman?

561
00:24:00,079 --> 00:24:01,279
What did you say?

562
00:24:07,119 --> 00:24:08,240
Your Highness, Crown Prince.

563
00:24:08,640 --> 00:24:10,400
General Li and I both feel

564
00:24:10,400 --> 00:24:12,279
that you should know about this.

565
00:24:12,799 --> 00:24:13,160
However,

566
00:24:14,200 --> 00:24:15,680
I know you well.

567
00:24:16,079 --> 00:24:17,880
If you'd rather not get involved,

568
00:24:18,319 --> 00:24:18,920
then this matter

569
00:24:19,559 --> 00:24:21,480
can be left to General Li and me.

570
00:24:22,279 --> 00:24:23,319
The Late Emperor doted

571
00:24:23,519 --> 00:24:24,519
upon the Crown Prince dearly.

572
00:24:24,519 --> 00:24:25,119
This fact

573
00:24:25,240 --> 00:24:26,680
was plain for everyone to see.

574
00:24:27,359 --> 00:24:28,200
Now,

575
00:24:28,279 --> 00:24:28,759
I...

576
00:24:30,920 --> 00:24:31,759
I will avenge my father's death

577
00:24:33,240 --> 00:24:34,880
with my own two hands.

578
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:40,839
Teacher,

579
00:24:42,359 --> 00:24:43,880
can you get in touch with Qi Zhi?

580
00:24:48,440 --> 00:24:49,920
I want to write him a letter.

581
00:24:51,160 --> 00:24:52,519
He is traveling around right now,

582
00:24:53,519 --> 00:24:54,440
so perhaps

583
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:56,759
he can trace the origin of this poison.

584
00:25:01,319 --> 00:25:02,119
Eunuch,

585
00:25:02,440 --> 00:25:03,359
work with me,

586
00:25:04,240 --> 00:25:05,440
and there's still a chance.

587
00:25:06,720 --> 00:25:08,119
You...

588
00:25:11,279 --> 00:25:12,559
You're rather interesting.
